metadata.description: Kazo Prestige Membership serves as your exclusive, private access pass to the Skylightz Collectibles' top tier membership, the Kazo Prestige. These 100 Kazo Prestige holders will be the Pioneer and Foundation members of the collectors' community that Skylightz Collectibles is building. These holders will play a huge and important role in this pivotal milestone in Skylightz Collectiblesâ€™ memory lane and will be locked into the token metadata on the Ethereum blockchain. In addition, Kazo Prestige holders get to unlock Lifetime 5% Storewide Discount in Skylightz Collectibles online store (except for items listed under challenges and mystery boxes), among a plethora of perks and privileges.
